  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Confirming Core Requirements**\n\nI\'ve got the initial build and linting clean. Now I am quickly re-familiarizing myself with the core project specifications. Specifically, I\'m checking that the initial React 18+ application with Vite and TypeScript is correctly initialized, and that dependencies like tailwindcss and react-hook-form are being installed. It looks good so far.\n\n\n**Validating Dependency Installation**\n\nI\'ve verified the installation of crucial dependencies: `@hookform/resolvers`, `zod`, `zustand`, `react-router-dom`, `react-dropzone`, `react-signature-canvas`, `cypress`, and `vitest`. I\'ve also confirmed compliance with the architectural specifications. The folder structure is in place, ESLint is configured with strict error handling, and the `MainLayout` component is implemented as specified. I\'ve also set up the Zustand store skeleton and basic routing. Finally, I\'ve created the `constants.ts` file. All good, no errors!\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have successfully initialized the React 18+ application using Vite and TypeScript. All dependencies have been installed, the folder structure has been created, and the application builds and lints with zero errors.\n\nHere is a summary of the accomplishments:\n- **Project Structure**: Created `src/components/`, `src/pages/`, `src/schemas/`, `src/store/`, `src/utils/`, `src/services/`, and `src/hooks/`.\n- **ESLint Configuration**: Configured with `eslint-config-airbnb`, `eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y`, and set to strict mode (zero warnings allowed).\n- **Zustand & Constants**: Scaffolded `formStore.ts` for step tracking and `constants.ts` for file sizes and loan limits.\n- **MainLayout**: Faithfully implemented the Stitch UI design using Tailwind CSS v4 variables, replacing Material icons with `lucide-react` components. The layout wraps a React Router `<Outlet />` to eventually handle the form steps seamlessly.\n- **Routing**: Updated `App.tsx` with `react-router-dom` to render `MainLayout`.\n\nAs requested, here are the configurations and `MainLayout.tsx` source code:\n\n### `package.json`\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"react-example\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"version\": \"0.0.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"dev\": \"vite --port=3000 --host=0.0.0.0\",\n    \"build\": \"vite build\",\n    \"preview\": \"vite preview\",\n    \"clean\": \"rm -rf dist server.js\",\n    \"lint\": \"ESLINT_USE_FLAT_CONFIG=false eslint src --ext .ts,.tsx --max-warnings 0\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@google/genai\": \"^2.4.0\",\n    \"@hookform/resolvers\": \"^5.4.0\",\n    \"@tailwindcss/vite\": \"^4.1.14\",\n    \"@vitejs/plugin-react\": \"^5.0.4\",\n    \"dotenv\": \"^17.2.3\",\n    \"express\": \"^4.21.2\",\n    \"lucide-react\": \"^0.546.0\",\n    \"motion\": \"^12.23.24\",\n    \"react\": \"^19.0.1\",\n    \"react-dom\": \"^19.0.1\",\n    \"react-dropzone\": \"^15.0.0\",\n    \"react-hook-form\": \"^7.80.0\",\n    \"react-router-dom\": \"^7.18.0\",\n    \"react-signature-canvas\": \"^1.1.0-alpha.2\",\n    \"vite\": \"^6.2.3\",\n    \"zod\": \"^4.4.3\",\n    \"zustand\": \"^5.0.14\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@types/express\": \"^4.17.21\",\n    \"@types/node\": \"^22.14.0\",\n    \"@types/react-signature-canvas\": \"^1.0.7\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin\": \"^7.18.0\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/parser\": \"^7.18.0\",\n    \"autoprefixer\": \"^10.4.21\",\n    \"cypress\": \"^15.18.0\",\n    \"esbuild\": \"^0.25.0\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^8.57.1\",\n    \"eslint-config-airbnb\": \"^19.0.4\",\n    \"eslint-config-airbnb-typescript\": \"^18.0.0\",\n    \"eslint-plugin-import\": \"^2.32.0\",\n    \"eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y\": \"^6.10.2\",\n    \"eslint-plugin-react\": \"^7.37.5\",\n    \"eslint-plugin-react-hooks\": \"^7.1.1\",\n    \"tailwindcss\": \"^4.1.14\",\n    \"tsx\": \"^4.21.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"~5.8.2\",\n    \"vite\": \"^6.2.3\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^4.1.9\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Vite & Tailwind Configuration (Tailwind v4 Uses `@theme` inside CSS)\n\n**`vite.config.ts`**\n```typescript\nimport tailwindcss from \'@tailwindcss/vite\';\nimport react from \'@vitejs/plugin-react\';\nimport path from \'path\';\nimport { defineConfig } from \'vite\';\n\nexport default defineConfig(() => {\n  return {\n    plugins: [react(), tailwindcss()],\n    resolve: {\n      alias: {\n        \'@\': path.resolve(__dirname, \'.\'),\n      },\n    },\n    // Server config ...\n  };\n});\n```\n\n**`src/index.css` (Tailwind Config Injection)**\n```css\n@import url(\'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Manrope:wght@600;700&display=swap\');\n@import \"tailwindcss\";\n\n@theme {\n  --color-on-primary-fixed-variant: #184974;\n  --color-surface-bright: #f8f9fa;\n  --color-inverse-on-surface: #f0f1f2;\n  --color-surface-variant: #e1e3e4;\n  --color-surface: #f8f9fa;\n  --color-on-tertiary-container: #ffa931;\n  --color-error: #ba1a1a;\n  --color-primary-container: #1f4e79;\n  --color-primary-fixed-dim: #a0cafc;\n  --color-secondary-container: #7bf8a1;\n  /* (All color variables defined...) */\n\n  --radius: 0.125rem;\n  --radius-lg: 0.25rem;\n  --radius-xl: 0.5rem;\n  --radius-full: 0.75rem;\n\n  --spacing-base: 4px;\n  --spacing-margin-desktop: 32px;\n  --spacing-xs: 4px;\n  --spacing-lg: 24px;\n  --spacing-xxl: 48px;\n  /* (All spacing variables defined...) */\n\n  --font-body-sm: \"Inter\", sans-serif;\n  --font-headline-lg-mobile: \"Manrope\", sans-serif;\n  /* (All fonts defined...) */\n\n  --text-body-sm: 14px;\n  --text-body-sm--line-height: 20px;\n  --text-body-sm--font-weight: 400;\n\n  --text-headline-lg-mobile: 24px;\n  --text-headline-lg-mobile--line-height: 32px;\n  --text-headline-lg-mobile--letter-spacing: -0.01em;\n  --text-headline-lg-mobile--font-weight: 700;\n  /* (All text sizing and heights defined...) */\n}\n```\n\n### `src/components/MainLayout.tsx`\n```tsx\nimport React from \'react\';\nimport { Outlet, NavLink } from \'react-router-dom\';\nimport {\n  Bell,\n  HelpCircle,\n  User,\n  Banknote,\n  Briefcase,\n  Landmark,\n  CreditCard,\n  FileText,\n  ShieldCheck,\n  Send,\n  Save,\n  ArrowLeft,\n  ArrowRight,\n} from \'lucide-react\';\n\nexport default function MainLayout() {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface bg-background\">\n      {/* Top Navigation Bar */}\n      <header className=\"fixed top-0 left-0 w-full z-50 flex justify-between items-center px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop h-16 bg-surface dark:bg-surface-dim font-body-md text-body-md border-b border-outline-variant dark:border-outline\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-md\">\n          <div className=\"w-8 h-8 rounded bg-primary flex items-center justify-center text-on-primary font-bold\">\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" className=\"w-5 h-5 text-secondary-fixed\">\n              <path d=\"M12 2L2 22h20L12 2z\" />\n            </svg>\n          </div>\n          <span className=\"font-headline-md text-headline-md font-bold text-primary dark:text-primary-fixed-dim hidden sm:block ml-2\">\n            LendSwift\n          </span>\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-sm\">\n          <button\n            type=\"button\"\n            aria-label=\"Notifications\"\n            className=\"p-sm text-on-surface-variant dark:text-surface-variant hover:bg-surface-container-low dark:hover:bg-surface-container-highest transition-colors rounded-full active:scale-95 transition-transform\"\n          >\n            <Bell className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n          </button>\n          <button\n            type=\"button\"\n            aria-label=\"Help\"\n            className=\"p-sm text-on-surface-variant dark:text-surface-variant hover:bg-surface-container-low dark:hover:bg-surface-container-highest transition-colors rounded-full active:scale-95 transition-transform\"\n          >\n            <HelpCircle className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n          </button>\n          <div\n            aria-label=\"User profile\"\n            className=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-surface-variant overflow-hidden ml-sm cursor-pointer hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors flex items-center justify-center\"\n          >\n            <User className=\"w-5 h-5 text-on-surface-variant\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </header>\n\n      <div className=\"flex flex-1 pt-16 pb-16 md:pb-0\">\n        {/* Side Navigation Bar (Desktop) */}\n        <nav className=\"fixed left-0 top-16 bottom-0 flex-col p-4 bg-surface-container-low dark:bg-surface-container-lowest font-label-md text-label-md border-r border-outline-variant dark:border-outline h-full w-64 hidden md:flex transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out z-40 overflow-y-auto\">\n          <div className=\"mb-lg\">\n            <h2 className=\"font-headline-sm text-headline-sm font-bold text-primary\">Loan Application</h2>\n            <p className=\"text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant mt-xs\">Application ID: LS-48291</p>\n          </div>\n          <ul className=\"flex-1 flex flex-col gap-xs space-y-2\">\n            <li>\n              <NavLink\n                to=\"/\"\n                className={({ isActive }) =>\n                  `flex items-center gap-md px-md py-sm rounded-lg w-full text-left transition-colors ${\n                    isActive\n                      ? \'bg-primary-container dark:bg-primary text-on-primary-container dark:text-on-primary font-semibold\'\n                      : \'text-on-surface-variant dark:text-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container-high dark:hover:bg-surface-variant\'\n                  }`\n                }\n              >\n                <User className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n                Identity Verification\n              </NavLink>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <button type=\"button\" className=\"flex items-center gap-md px-md py-sm text-on-surface-variant dark:text-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container-high dark:hover:bg-surface-variant rounded-lg w-full text-left transition-colors\">\n                <Banknote className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n                Income Details\n              </button>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <button type=\"button\" className=\"flex items-center gap-md px-md py-sm text-on-surface-variant dark:text-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container-high dark:hover:bg-surface-variant rounded-lg w-full text-left transition-colors\">\n                <Briefcase className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n                Employment Status\n              </button>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <button type=\"button\" className=\"flex items-center gap-md px-md py-sm text-on-surface-variant dark:text-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container-high dark:hover:bg-surface-variant rounded-lg w-full text-left transition-colors\">\n                <Landmark className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n                Asset Disclosure\n              </button>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <button type=\"button\" className=\"flex items-center gap-md px-md py-sm text-on-surface-variant dark:text-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container-high dark:hover:bg-surface-variant rounded-lg w-full text-left transition-colors\">\n                <CreditCard className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n                Liability Review\n              </button>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <button type=\"button\" className=\"flex items-center gap-md px-md py-sm text-on-surface-variant dark:text-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container-high dark:hover:bg-surface-variant rounded-lg w-full text-left transition-colors\">\n                <FileText className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n                Loan Purpose\n              </button>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <button type=\"button\" className=\"flex items-center gap-md px-md py-sm text-on-surface-variant dark:text-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container-high dark:hover:bg-surface-variant rounded-lg w-full text-left transition-colors\">\n                <ShieldCheck className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n                Security Selection\n              </button>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <button type=\"button\" className=\"flex items-center gap-md px-md py-sm text-on-surface-variant dark:text-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container-high dark:hover:bg-surface-variant rounded-lg w-full text-left transition-colors\">\n                <Send className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n                Final Submission\n              </button>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n          <div className=\"mt-auto pt-md border-t border-outline-variant\">\n            <button type=\"button\" className=\"w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-sm px-md py-sm text-primary font-label-md hover:bg-surface-container-high rounded-lg transition-colors border border-primary\">\n              <Save className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n              Save for later\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        </nav>\n\n        {/* Main Content Area */}\n        <main className=\"flex-1 md:ml-64 p-margin-mobile md:p-margin-desktop w-full max-w-[1024px] mx-auto\">\n          {/* Mobile Horizontal Stepper */}\n          <div className=\"md:hidden flex overflow-x-auto space-x-4 pb-4 mb-6 border-b border-outline-variant\" style={{ scrollbarWidth: \'none\' }}>\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center min-w-[80px]\">\n              <div className=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary text-on-primary flex items-center justify-center font-label-sm mb-1\">1</div>\n              <span className=\"font-label-sm text-primary\">Identity</span>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center min-w-[80px] opacity-50\">\n              <div className=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-outline text-on-surface-variant flex items-center justify-center font-label-sm mb-1\">2</div>\n              <span className=\"font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant\">Income</span>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center min-w-[80px] opacity-50\">\n              <div className=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-outline text-on-surface-variant flex items-center justify-center font-label-sm mb-1\">3</div>\n              <span className=\"font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant\">Employment</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <Outlet />\n        </main>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Bottom Navigation Bar (Actions) */}\n      <footer className=\"fixed bottom-0 left-0 w-full z-50 flex justify-between items-center h-16 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-surface dark:bg-surface-dim font-label-sm text-label-sm border-t border-outline-variant dark:border-outline transition-transform md:ml-64 md:w-[calc(100%-256px)]\">\n        <button type=\"button\" className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-xs md:gap-sm px-md py-xs md:py-sm text-on-surface-variant dark:text-surface-variant hover:bg-surface-container-low dark:hover:bg-surface-container-highest rounded-lg transition-colors border border-outline\">\n          <ArrowLeft className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n          <span className=\"hidden md:inline font-label-md\">Back</span>\n        </button>\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-sm md:gap-md\">\n          <button type=\"button\" className=\"hidden md:flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-xs md:gap-sm px-md py-xs md:py-sm text-primary font-label-md hover:bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg transition-colors\">\n            <Save className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n            <span>Save Draft</span>\n          </button>\n          <button type=\"button\" className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-xs md:gap-sm px-xl py-sm md:py-sm bg-primary text-on-primary font-label-md hover:bg-primary-container hover:text-on-primary-container rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-sm\">\n            <span className=\"hidden md:inline\">Next Step</span>\n            <ArrowRight className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </footer>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n```"
